functional_requirements.description:
SSE 事件格式标准化：7 种事件类型的 data 字段统一为结构化 JSON。
- agent_started → {agentName, analysisId, timestamp}
- agent_state_update → {agentName, status, progress, intermediateResult, durationMs}
- agent_completed → {agentName, analysisId, result, timestamp}
- agent_failed → {agentName, error, timestamp}
- analysis_completed → {analysisId, status, report, citations}
- error → {type, message}
- ping → {timestamp}

api_contracts.response_format:
text/event-stream with 7 standardized event types:
- event: agent_started
data: {"agentName":"...","analysisId":"...","timestamp":"ISO8601"}

- event: agent_state_update
data: {"agentName":"...","status":"running","progress":0.5,"intermediateResult":"...","durationMs":1234}

- event: agent_completed
data: {"agentName":"...","analysisId":"...","result":{...},"timestamp":"ISO8601"}

- event: agent_failed
data: {"agentName":"...","error":"...","timestamp":"ISO8601"}

- event: analysis_completed
data: {"analysisId":"...","status":"completed","report":"...","citations":[...]}

- event: error
data: {"type":"timeout|internal","message":"..."}

- event: ping
data: {"timestamp":"ISO8601"}
